t extraction\n81: \n82: - [x] T016 `git mv` `027/.../003-skill-advisor-cli/` to `system-skill-advisor/008-skill-advisor-cli/`\n83: - [x] T017 Extract 8 advisor-only items from `027/003-advisor-and-codegraph/` into `system-skill-advisor/009-advisor-and-codegraph-migrated-items/`\n84: - [x] T018 `git mv` `027/.../021-system-skill-advisor` to `system-skill-advisor/010-skill-advisor-frontmatter-alignment/`\n85: - [x] T019 Renumber `027/003-advisor-and-codegraph/002-xce-feature-adoption-advisor-codegraph`'s remaining children `001-004`, update parent spec.md prose\n86: - [x] T020 Reconcile `027/004-shared-infrastructure/001-mcp-to-cli-tool-transition/` and `027/000-release-cleanup/009-skill-frontmatter-alignment/` (contiguous renumber, 20+ siblings)\n87: - [x] T021 `validate.sh --strict --recursive` on `027/` and `system-skill-advisor/008-010`\n88: \n89: ### Batch 2d: 028 hub + destination renumber\n90: \n91: - [x] T022 `git mv` `028/002-skill-advisor/` to `system-skill-advisor/011-skill-advisor-phase-parent/`\n92: - [x] T023 Renumber `028`'s remaining top-level children `003→002, 004→003, 005→004, 006→005`\n93: - [x] T024 Rename `system-skill-advisor/001-skill-advisor-tuning/` to `012-skill-advisor-tuning/`, fix all `001`-referencing metadata fields to `012`\n94: - [x] T025 `validate.sh --strict --recursive` on `028/` and `system-skill-advisor/011-012`\n95: \n96: ### Batch 2e: Destination track finalization\n97: \n98: - [x] T026 Rewrite `system-skill-advisor/spec.md` (track root) to narrate the full 001-012 history\n99: - [x] T027 Write `system-skill-advisor/context-index.md` documenting the 6 left-in-place shared/joint items\n100: - [x] T028 Regenerate `system-skill-advisor/description.json` + `graph-metadata.json` for the full 001-012 children set\n101: <!-- /ANCHOR:phase-2 -->\n102: \n103: ---\n104: \n105: <!-- ANCHOR:phase-3 -->\n106: ## Phase 3: Verification\n107: \n108: - [x] T029 `validate.sh --strict --recursive` clean on `system-skill-advisor/`, `026/`, `027/`,